.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-opencode/assets/scripts/test_verify_alignment_drift.py:6:"""Unit-style coverage for verify_alignment_drift.py behavior."""
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-opencode/assets/scripts/test_verify_alignment_drift.py:18:SCRIPT_PATH = Path(__file__).resolve().parent / "verify_alignment_drift.py"
.opencode/skills/sk-code/code-opencode/assets/scripts/test_verify_alignment_drift.py:22:    spec = importlib.util.spec_from_file_location("verify_alignment_drift", SCRIPT_PATH)
