.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/tasks.md:54:- [ ] T011 Integrate eligible route-gold rows into `run-skill-benchmark.cjs` without changing D1-D5 aggregation. (REQ-005) {deps: T008-T010}
.opencode/specs/sk-doc/019-sk-doc-router-alignment/020-router-unification-program/007-unified-refactor-implementation/014-benchmark-alignment/tasks.md:66:- [ ] T014 Verify fresh eligible scenarios run flag-on and pass legacy gold, compiled gold, and mutual routing equality. (REQ-002, REQ-003, REQ-007)
